'''Cannabis in Greenland''' is illegal, but is used illicitly in the country. Scholarly works in 2010 and 2015 noted increasing cannabis crime in the nation.<ref name="Newman2010">{{cite book|author=Graeme R. Newman|title=Crime and Punishment around the World &#91;4 volumes&#93;: &#91;Four Volumes&#93;|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2uK6bR9byVIC&pg=RA1-PA160|date=19 October 2010|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-0-313-35134-1|pages=1–}}</ref><ref name="Breum2015">{{cite book|author=Martin Breum|title=The Greenland Dilemma: The quest for independence, the underground riches and the troubled relations with Denmark|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1vlvCQAAQBAJ&pg=PT46|date=20 May 2015|publisher=Royal Danish Defence College|isbn=978-87-7147-099-4|pages=46–}}</ref>

